data.description: Escape the busyness of the city and live the peaceful life you've dreamed of...Welcome to a cozy well maintained 3Br/2Ba cabin 1352 sq ft. on 2 acres in the beautiful Prescott National Forest.  Large windows to take in the amazing views, wrap around upstairs deck. Enjoy your morning coffee in the screened in deck while listening to the wind and birds chirping and evening meals while taking in amazing sunsets. Cuddle up in front of a wood burning fireplace in the evenings. Wood flooring, 2 car garage with a separate room above (currently being used as a sewing room/craft room/office, could be a study or man cave, possibilities only limited by your imagination). Central heat H/A and Whole house generator for pease of mind.
